{
  "schemaVersion": "1.1.0",
  "id": "data-transformation-export-transformations",
  "title": "Export your transformations",
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "By default, Grafana Cloud doesn't support exporting data transformations directly to an external database or other tools. However, you can export the transformation manually as a CSV file."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "To export the data transformations, open an existing panel with transformations applied in edit mode on your dashboard."
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "button[data-testid='data-testid Tab Queries']",
          "content": "Click the **Queries** tab.",
          "requirements": ["exists-reftarget", "on-page:/d/"]
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "button",
          "reftarget": "Query inspector",
          "content": "Click **Query inspector**.",
          "requirements": ["exists-reftarget"]
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "button[data-testid='data-testid Tab Data']",
          "content": "Select the **Data** tab.",
          "requirements": ["exists-reftarget"]
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "div:text('Data options')",
          "content": "Expand the **Data options** row.",
          "requirements": ["exists-reftarget"]
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "label:text('Apply panel transformations')",
          "content": "Enable the **Apply panel transformations** option.",
          "requirements": ["exists-reftarget"]
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "button",
          "reftarget": "Download CSV",
          "content": "Click **Download CSV**.",
          "requirements": ["exists-reftarget"]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "A CSV file containing the data set with transformations applied downloads to your machine.\n\nIn the next milestone, you'll wrap up this learning path."
    }
  ]
}
